PHONE_REDACTEDT09:PORT:PORT.499487Z	   14 Query	insert into daily_analysis_reports (analysis_confidence,analysis_scope_note,day,executive_summary,generated_at,misconfiguration_signals,system_behavior_analysis,user_behavior_analysis) values ('This analysis is based on data from a single day and should be considered preliminary, as trends may not necessarily continue over longer periods.','The scope of this analysis covers the specified date (PHONE_REDACTED) only.','PHONE_REDACTED','On the analyzed day (PHONE_REDACTED), a total of 195 lead submissions were made, with 75.90% being successful. The majority of attempts were originated from the website form. EMAIL_REDACTED and EMAIL_REDACTED had the highest activity but also experienced failure rates of 15.28% and 29.27% respectively.','PHONE_REDACTED:PORT:PORT.488545','The high number of duplicate submissions suggests possible issues with lead validation or handling in the system. The presence of rate limit exceeded errors indicates potential misconfigurations related to submission throttling.','The system handled a maximum of 20 attempts per minute and showed a burst of high activity in one minute. Duplicate lead submissions and rate limit exceeded errors were observed, accounting for 42 and 5 failures respectively.','EMAIL_REDACTED and EMAIL_REDACTED were active, with user2 making 72 attempts (including 11 failures) and user1 making 123 attempts (including 36 failures).')
